## 🧪 Week 1: Mark-and-Sweep GC 구현

### 핵심 개념

**Mark Phase**:
```
1. Root objects 확인 (stack, globals)
2. Reachable objects 모두 추적 (DFS)
3. Marked flag 설정
```

**Sweep Phase**:
```
1. Heap 전체 스캔
2. Unmarked objects 회수
3. Free list 업데이트
```

### 구현 계획

#### 1️⃣ HeapObject 구조 추가 (src/vm.rs)

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
struct HeapObject {
    address: usize,          // Heap address
    size: usize,             // Size in words
    allocated: bool,         // Currently allocated
    marked: bool,            // Mark phase flag
    object_type: ObjectType, // Array or String
}

enum ObjectType {
    Array(usize),   // size
    String(usize),  // length
}
```

